settings.title:
Auto Dustbin Cleaning
for True Automation
settings.content:
Compatible with:
yeedi vac series (vac / vac max / vac station)
yeedi vac 2 series (vac 2 / vac 2 pro)

settings.title: Self-Empties the Dustbin
settings.content:
No more frequent dustbin emptying.
yeedi self-empty station automatically cleans the dustbin
for a truly hands-free cleaning experience.

settings.title:
Effective Pollutants
Capturing
settings.content:
Triple-layer structured dust bag with sub-high
efficiency filter material captures pollutants
as small as 0.3 microns to keep your home
clean and fresh.

settings.title: Sealing Design
settings.content:
The dust bag with an extra rubber ring
automatically seals when reomoved from
the station to avoid leakage.

settings.title:
One-Click Emptying
in 30 Days
settings.content:
yeedi's 2.5L dust bag seals up to 30 days worth of dust<br class="br_pc">
in place so you can forget about vacuuming<br class="br_pc">
for a whole month.

settings.title: Devour Dirt in 20s
settings.content:
With 27,000Pa suction power, yeedi self-empty station<br class="br_pc">
easily sucks up the dirt from the dustbin<br class="br_pc">
into the dust bag in merely 20s.

settings.title: Dust Bag Detection
settings.content:
Equipped with high accuracy sensors, yeedi self-empty station will remind you<br class="br_pc">
to replace the dust bag once it's full to prevent leaks.

settings.title: Customizable Settings
settings.content:
Set the self-emptying frequency between Standard,<br class="br_pc"> 
High Frequency, and Do Not Disturb modes<br class="br_pc">
as per your needs.
